manufacturing.value:
Manufacturing:
RoHS and lead free compliant manufacturing process

Board thickness: 1.6 mm
Material: FR4 35/35 um copper
Silkscreen: top (white), bottom (white)
Soldermask: top (green), bottom (green)
Surface finish: ENIG (lead free)
